	<h1 class="title">460 多万元，在纽约可以买个啥房？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">C. J. Hughes</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-23 15:36:12 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/5514/medium/5514.jpg?1436687959" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


